issue.title: add flags for configuration files not only PWD
issue.body: Consider to use other path then PWD , so that an user could pass the path as flag to the binary.

issue.title: catch already running jobs
issue.body:
When scheduling new jobs to scheduler we should consider to don't add a job which is already in the schedule plan.

https://github.com/MalloZup/fullrocketmetal/blob/master/src/fullrocketmetal/core.clj#L37

Consider to add specific UID under control for this.

release.name: initial releases
release.body:
# info:

the 1st release let users describe a message which will scheduled regularly defined by crontab (quartz) syntax.

issue.title: quartz: enable debug info to be printed or stored
issue.body:
The quartz scheduler can go wrong on scheduling job/triggers for some reasons.

We should enable debug info.

Investigate if with quarzite is possible
